<li id="cite_note-88"><b><a href="#cite_ref-88" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.hpc.ncep.noaa.gov/html/about2.shtml" class="external text" title="http://www.hpc.ncep.noaa.gov/html/about2.shtml" rel="nofollow">About the HPC</a>, NOAA/ National Weather Service, National Centers for Environmental Prediction, <a href="http://www.hpc.ncep.noaa.gov/" class="external text" title="http://www.hpc.ncep.noaa.gov/" rel="nofollow">Hydrometeorological Prediction Center</a>, Camp Springs, Maryland, 2007.</li>
<li id="cite_note--89"><b><a href="#cite_ref-_89-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.springerlink.com/index/R55V691512754216.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.springerlink.com/index/R55V691512754216.pdf" rel="nofollow">"Modern research in nuclear meteorology"</a> (PDF). <i>Atomic Energy</i>. Springer New York. February 1974. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1007%2FBF01117823" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1007%2FBF01117823" rel="nofollow">10.1007/BF01117823</a></span><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.springerlink.com/index/R55V691512754216.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.springerlink.com/index/R55V691512754216.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.springerlink.com/index/R55V691512754216.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on July 6 2008</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Modern+research+in+nuclear+meteorology&amp;rft.atitle=Atomic+Energy&amp;rft.date=February+1974&amp;rft.pub=Springer+New+York&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1007%2FBF01117823&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.springerlink.com%2Findex%2FR55V691512754216.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Meteorology"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
