te)">Aura</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/CloudSat" title="CloudSat">CloudSat</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/CALIPSO" title="CALIPSO">CALIPSO</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Hydros" title="Hydros">Hydros</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/NPOESS" title="NPOESS">NPOESS</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Earth_System_Science_Pathfinder&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Earth System Science Pathfinder (page does not exist)">ESSP</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Aquarius_(satellite)" title="Aquarius (satellite)">Aquarius</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/New_Millennium_program" title="New Millennium program">NMP</a>/EO-3</span></div>
